sequenceDiagram
    participant C as API Consumer
    participant R as ClientResource
    participant S as ClientService
    participant CS as CountryService
    participant RC as RestCountriesClient
    participant DB as ClientRepository
    participant H2 as Database

    Note over C,H2: POST /api/v1/clients (Create)
    C->>R: POST JSON body
    R->>R: Bean Validation
    R->>S: createClient(request)
    S->>DB: existsByEmail(email)
    DB->>H2: SELECT COUNT
    H2-->>DB: 0
    DB-->>S: false
    S->>DB: existsByPhone(phone)
    DB->>H2: SELECT COUNT
    H2-->>DB: 0
    DB-->>S: false
    S->>CS: getDemonym(countryCode)
    CS->>RC: GET /alpha/{code}
    RC-->>CS: CountryData[]
    CS-->>S: "American"
    S->>DB: persist(client)
    DB->>H2: INSERT
    S->>DB: flush()
    DB->>H2: COMMIT
    S-->>R: Client entity
    R-->>C: 201 ApiResponse + Location

    Note over C,H2: DELETE /api/v1/clients/:uuid (Soft Delete)
    C->>R: DELETE
    R->>S: deleteClient(uuid)
    S->>DB: findActiveByUuid(uuid)
    DB->>H2: SELECT WHERE active=true
    H2-->>DB: Client
    DB-->>S: Optional(Client)
    S->>S: client.active = false
    S-->>R: void
    R-->>C: 200 ApiResponse
